sentence: Susan Wojcicki, Director at salesforce.com Inc. ( CRM ), bought 1,356 shares of the company's common stock on September 19.
The shares were purchased at $73.71 for a total of $99,950.76.
IK-> The technicals for CRM ($73.22 up $0.21) are bullish with a neutral trend.
Support has been around $73.06 and resistance around $73.99.
Look at the November 55/60 bull-put spread for a 20-cent credit.
That's a 4.2% return and the stock has to fall 18.1% to cause a problem.
